text: A safe-cracker is a person capable of opening a safe without either the combination or the key. It may also refer to: *Safecracker, a 1997 video game **Safecracker: The Ultimate Puzzle Adventure, its 2006 spiritual successor *Safecracker (pinball), the Bally pinball game from 1996 *"The Safe-Cracker", an episode of Life on Mars ==See also== *Henschel Hs 129, a German Luftwaffe Aircraft
title: Safe-cracker (disambiguation)
